How Gautam Adani became India's second-richest person being first-generation entrepreneur. He didn't build businesses; he acquired them and revamped them. 

Adani recognised the value of established assets. He focused on infrastructure and essential industries. Where others saw obstacles, Adani saw opportunity. With moves that transformed ports, power, and logistics, he laid the groundwork for an empire that spans industries—from seaports to airports, mining to manufacturing.

Today, he’s not just a business magnate; he’s the King of Infrastructure, a visionary who plays on a scale that has made his name synonymous with ambition and growth.

How Adani built stable revenue streams and gave his business a new footing through long-term contracts, networking, and opportunity scanning? In this 12th episode of “Tycoons of India”, Dr Vivek Bindra explains in detail the 9 business strategies that played a key role in Adani's success-

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
There's no stopping the game.

Squid Game Season 2 on December 26, 2024.

Only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won.

Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys® becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81203480

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 283 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Heralding the return of the worldwide hit, a new chapter unfolds as Gi-hun comes back with an agenda, having given up on leaving for the US.

Lakshami Mata Aarti Lyrics (Hindi & English)

ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता,
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata,

मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता ।
Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुमको निसदिन सेवत,
Tumko nisdin sevat,

हर विष्णु विधाता ।
Har Vishnu Vidhata.

उमा, रमा, ब्रम्हाणी,
Uma, Rama, Brahmani,

तुम ही जग माता ।
Tum hi Jag Mata.

सूर्य चद्रंमा ध्यावत,
Surya Chandrama Dhyavat,

नारद ऋषि गाता ।
Narad Rishi Gaata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

दुर्गा रूप निरंजनि,
Durga Roop Niranjani,

सुख-संपत्ति दाता ।
Sukh-Sampatti Daata.

जो कोई तुमको ध्याता,
Jo Koi Tumko Dhyata,

ऋद्धि-सिद्धि धन पाता ।
Riddhi-Siddhi Dhan Paata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

तुम ही पाताल निवासनी,
Tum hi Pataal Nivasini,

तुम ही शुभदाता ।
Tum hi Shubhadaata.

कर्म-प्रभाव-प्रकाशनी,
Karma-Prabhav-Prakashini,

भव निधि की त्राता ।
Bhav Nidhi Ki Traata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

जिस घर तुम रहती हो,
Jis Ghar Tum Rehti Ho,

ताँहि में हैं सद्गुण आता ।
Tahin Mein Hain Sadgun Aata.

सब सम्भव हो जाता,
Sab Sambhav Ho Jaata,

मन नहीं घबराता ।
Man Nahin Ghabraata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

तुम बिन यज्ञ ना होता,
Tum Bin Yagya Na Hota,

वस्त्र न कोई पाता ।
Vastra Na Koi Paata.

खान पान का वैभव,
Khan Paan Ka Vaibhav,

सब तुमसे आता ।
Sab Tumse Aata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

शुभ गुण मंदिर सुंदर,
Shubh Gun Mandir Sundar,

क्षीरोदधि जाता ।
Ksheerodadhi Jaata.

रत्न चतुर्दश तुम बिन,
Ratna Chaturdash Tum Bin,

कोई नहीं पाता ।
Koi Nahin Paata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

महालक्ष्मी जी की आरती,
Mahalakshmi Ji Ki Aarti,

जो कोई नर गाता ।
Jo Koi Nar Gaata.

उर आनंद समाता,
Ur Anand Samaata,

पाप उतर जाता ।
Paap Utar Jaata.

॥ ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता...॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata...

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In today's video we explore, India’s ambitious initiative to transform the arid Thar Desert into a lush green forest! We talk about the innovative strategies, groundbreaking technologies, and community efforts driving this incredible environmental change. However, is this change truly in the benefit of India? Well, let's see...

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4232 | 2 Nov 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4232: Sarees For Mahila Mandal
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal invites the Mahila Mandal to his house and gifts them sarees for Diwali. Meanwhile, the men of Gokuldham gather at Abdul's shop. Later, Bhide announces that free firecrackers will be given to all society members.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4232 | 2 Nov 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000295792

snippet.title: Indians And Diwali | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
Happy Diwali to all of you , may this diwali brings joy , laughter , prosperity 

As the Title is Indians And Diwali this Video has everything that happens during Diwali Festival . The most relatable and Funny Diwali Video . Scenarios like what happens on Indian families doing Diwali shopping for dhanteras shopping new utensils or jewellery shopping of gold coin , silver coin from brand like Tanishq . Kaamwali and her struggles with house cleaning waiting for diwali gifts , diwali bonus . Daughter painting diya and mom hanging diwali lights . Girls dressing up in traditional dieting whole month to look good and clicking pictures and making videos . Preparations for office diwali pooja , sisters cleaning house and competing and having fun , next day of diwali and taking off the lights , flower garlands , rangoli , giving diwali to staff , guards , kaamwali bai , Aunties for shopping for diwali pooja kheel patashe , patisha , paan , supari , sweets , favourite mathai moti choor ladoo , kaju ki barfi , bondi ke laddoo , cham cham , diwali decoration , bhandan var , diya , lights , candles , rangoli , diwali gifts dry fruits , gift box . Indian Aunties bargaining with shopkeeper , shops making huge profits during diwali dhamaka sales , going out to relatives to wish happy diwali and dealing with diwali 2024 traffic jams , giving gifts to relatives and travelling in car , indian sweets shops fully loaded with customers , eating in restaurants after diwali shopping , shopkeeper selling bandhanbar , latkane , diwali decorations , eating dosa , chowmein , work from home people busy with job and ghar ki safai , tuition mam helps kids prepare their diwali poem , diwali essay , teaching why diwali is celebrated , diwali school function costumes , diwali is the festival food , every foodie loves puri , mathi , samosa , ladoo , aloo , kheer , halwa , muli ki bhujji , raita , achar , panchamrit , laxmi ganesh pooja , house aura cleansing with diwali aarti , talking about the ban on fire crackers , diwali away from home , pg wali diwali , showing off chandi , gold gifts , buying air purifier cause of the air pollution and noise pullution caused by crackers in delhi , south delhi posh diwali partiers playing poker , drinking , tambola , diwali vlogs , diwali outfits , lehenga , suits , saree , kurti , kurta , and looking beautiful and clicking pictures . West Delhi people mocking south delhi on dieting on diwali doing keto , intermittent fasting or just drinking alcohol , many more fun things covered in the diwali video .
This video is filled with Festive season memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories of Diwali festival
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour . A very happy diwali 2024 season to all of you and Happy deepawali  .. Comment down your Fav Part , 
Like , Share and

snippet.title: சஷ்டி முதல் நாள் விரதம் துவங்கும் முறை | இந்த 4 வரி பதிகம் உங்கள் வாழ்க்கையை மாற்றும் | Sashti Day 1
snippet.description:
#kandhasashti #sashti #sashtifasting #sashtiviratham #mahakandhasashti #kandhasashtiviratham #kandhasaahtiviradham #கந்தசஷ்டிவிரதம் #சஷ்டி #சஷ்டிவிரதம் #மகாகந்தசஷ்டி 

கந்த சஷ்டி விரதம் 2024 - துவங்கும் நாள், நேரம் & கடைப்பிடிக்கும் முறை | Kandha Sashti Viratham 2024
https://youtu.be/PEd1isXj02c

குழந்தைப்பேறு அருளும் திருப்புகழ் 

செகமாயை யுற்றெ னகவாழ்வில் வைத்த
திருமாது கெர்ப்ப             முடலூறித்

தெசமாத முற்றி வடிவாய்நி லத்தில்
திரமாய ளித்த             பொருளாகி

மகவாவி னுச்சி விழியாந நத்தில்
மலைநேர்பு யத்தி          லுறவாடி

மடிமீத டுத்து விளையாடி நித்த
மணிவாயின் முத்தி        தரவேணும்

முகமாய மிட்ட குறமாதி னுக்கு
முலைமேல ணைக்க       வருநீதா

முதுமாம றைக்கு ளொருமாபொ ருட்குள்
மொழியேயு ரைத்த         குருநாதா

தகையாதெ னக்கு னடிகாண வைத்த
தனியேர கத்தின்            முருகோனே

தருகாவி ரிக்கு வடபாரி சத்தில்
சமர்வேலெ டுத்த            பெருமாளே.

SEGA MAYAI UTRE NAGA VAZHVIL VAITHTHA
THIRUMADHU GERBAM       UDAL URI

THESAMADHA MUTRI VADIVAY NILATHTHIL
THIRAMAY ALITHTHA       PORULAGI

MAGAVAVIN UCHCHI VIZHI ANANATHTHIL
MALAI NER BUYATHTHIL       URAVADI

MADIMEE DHADUTHTHU VILAIYADI NITHTHAM
MANIVAYIN MUTHTHI       THARAVENUM

MUGA MAYAM ITTA KURA MADHINUKKU
MULAIMEL ANAIKKA       VARU NEEDHA

MUDHU MA MARAIKKUL ORU MA PORUTKUL
MOZHIYE URAITHTHA       GURUNATHA

THAGAIYADH ENAKKUN ADI KANA VAITHTHA
THANI ERAGATHTHIN       MURUGONE

THARU KAVIRIKKU VADA PARISATHTHIL
SAMAR VEL EDUTHTHA       PERUMALE.

4 வரி பதிகம் - இந்தப் பதிகத்தை பாராயணம் செய்து முருகப்பெருமானை சரணடையுங்கள்.

உன்னை ஒழிய ஒருவரையும் நம்புகிலேன்
பின்னை ஒருவரையான் பின்செல்லேன் - பன்னிருகைக்
கோலப்பா! வானோர் கொடியவினை தீர்த்தருளும்
வேலப்பா! செந்தில் வாழ்வே!

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

IPL 2025 Retentions: Full list of retained and released players by all 10 franchises ahead of mega auction.
The road to the 2025 IPL season is well underway, as the ten franchises announced their retention lists ahead of the big auction set to occur before the close of the year. In an IPL Retention Special on JioCinema, the teams announced which players will continue to represent their jerseys in the tournament next year — but also some big names who will be going under the hammer in the auction, who teams will keep an eye on.
Heinrich Klaasen was the highest earner in the retention lists, with Sunrisers Hyderabad giving him 23 crore to keep his services. Virat Kohli and Nicholas Pooran were right behind, as RCB and LSG give them INR 21 cr each.
On the other hands, some big-name players will be seeking new homes in the auction. Amongst these are Delhi franchise hero Rishabh Pant who was confirmed as released in a shock move, as well as KL Rahul, KKR title-winning captain Shreyas Iyer, and a premium Indian fast bowler in the form of Arshdeep Singh as well. They are joined by some big-name overseas players as well, headed by Jos Buttler and Glenn Maxwell.
Punjab Kings retained the fewest players, and Ricky Ponting will have a warchest of 110.5 cr in the auction, by far the most in this year’s auction. RCB will also have 83 crore on hand with only three retentions, while DC will have 73 cr under their new leadership as well. KKR and RR will both head into the auction with the maximum of six players already in their squads, but the Jaipur team will have only 41 cr to work with at the auction, with no RTM possibilities either.

IPL Retention List of all teams ahead of IPL 2025 mega auction

The Indian Premier League (IPL) 2025 retention list is here! Teams are revealing their retained players with surprising picks and releases.
It’s official! The retention lists for all franchises are now being revealed one by one for the Indian Premier League (IPL) 2025. After months of planning and strategizing on whom to retain and whom to release, the franchises have finalized their choices. Here is the list of all retained players from each franchise for IPL 2025.

Each franchise can retain up to six players from their 2024 squad ahead of the mega auction, with a maximum of five being capped internationals (either Indian or overseas) and up to two uncapped Indian players. This retention limit allows teams to maintain a solid core as they prepare for the upcoming IPL season.

CSK - Ruturaj Gaikwad (18cr), Matheesha Pathirana (13cr), Shivam Dube (12cr), Ravindra Jadeja (18cr), MS Dhoni (4cr) (uncapped)
MI - Hardik Pandya (c) (16.35cr), Rohit Sharma (16.30cr), Suryakumar Yadav(16.35cr), Jasprit Bumrah (18cr), Tilak Varma (11cr)
RCB - Virat Kohli (21cr), Rajat Patidar (11cr), Yash Dayal (5cr)
RR - Sanju Samson (18cr), Yashasvi Jaiswal (18cr), Riyan Parag (14cr) and Sandeep Sharma (4cr) (uncapped), Shimron Hetmyer (11cr), Dhruv Jurel (14cr)
LSG - Nicholas Pooran, Mayank Yadav, Ravi Bishnoi and Mohsin Khan (upcapped) Ayush Badoni (uncapped)
SRH - Heinrich Klaasen (23 cr), Pat Cummins (18 Cr), Abhishek Sharma (14cr), Nitish Reddy (6cr) and Travis Head (14cr)
PBKS - Shashank Singh (uncapped) (5.5cr) Prabhsimran Singh (uncapped) (4cr)
GT - Rashid Khan (18 cr), Shubman Gill (16.5cr), Sai Sudharsan (8.5cr), Rahul Tewatia (4cr), Shahrukh Khan (4 cr)
KKR - Rinku Singh (18 Cr) Varun Chakaravarthy (14 Cr), Sunil Narine (11 Cr), Andre Russell (18 Cr), Harshit Rana (Uncapped, Rs 4 Cr), Ramandeep Singh (Uncapped, Rs 4 Cr)
DC - Axar Patel, Kuldeep Yadav, Tristan Stubbs, Abhishek Porel (uncapped)

IPL Retention List of all teams ahead of IPL 2025 mega auction

The Indian Premier League (IPL) 2025 retention list is here! Teams are revealing their retained players with surprising picks and releases.
It’s official! The retention lists for all franchises are now being revealed one by one for the Indian Premier League (IPL) 2025. After months of planning and strategizing on whom to retain and whom to release, the franchises have finalized their choices. Here is the list of all retained players from each franchise for IPL 2025.

Each franchise can retain up to six players from their 2024 squad ahead of the mega auction, with a maximum of five being capped internationals (either Indian or overseas) and up to two uncapped Indian players. This retention limit allows teams to maintain a solid core as they prepare for the upcoming IPL season.

CSK - Ruturaj Gaikwad (18cr), Matheesha Pathirana (13cr), Shivam Dube (12cr), Ravindra Jadeja (18cr), MS Dhoni (4cr) (uncapped)
MI - Hardik Pandya (c) (16.35cr), Rohit Sharma (16.30cr), Suryakumar Yadav(16.35cr), Jasprit Bumrah (18cr), Tilak Varma (11cr)
RCB - Virat Kohli (21cr), Rajat Patidar (11cr), Yash Dayal (5cr)
RR - Sanju Samson (18cr), Yashasvi Jaiswal (18cr), Riyan Parag (14cr) and Sandeep Sharma (4cr) (uncapped), Shimron Hetmyer (11cr), Dhruv Jurel (14cr)
LSG - Nicholas Pooran, Mayank Yadav, Ravi Bishnoi and Mohsin Khan (upcapped) Ayush Badoni (uncapped)
SRH - Heinrich Klaasen (23 cr), Pat Cummins (18 Cr), Abhishek Sharma (14cr), Nitish Reddy (6cr) and Travis Head (14cr)
PBKS - Shashank Singh (uncapped) (5.5cr) Prabhsimran Singh (uncapped) (4cr)
GT - Rashid Khan (18 cr), Shubman Gill (16.5cr), Sai Sudharsan (8.5cr), Rahul Tewatia (4cr), Shahrukh Khan (4 cr)
KKR - Rinku Singh (18 Cr) Varun Chakaravarthy (14 Cr), Sunil Narine (11 Cr), Andre Russell (18 Cr), Harshit Rana (Uncapped, Rs 4 Cr), Ramandeep Singh (Uncapped, Rs 4 Cr)
DC - Axar Patel, Kuldeep Yadav, Tristan Stubbs, Abhishek Porel (uncapped)

snippet.title: A Very Special Diwali | Rahul Gandhi
snippet.description:
एक यादगार दिवाली, खास लोगों के साथ - ये दिवाली कुछ पेंटर भाइयों के साथ काम कर, एक कुम्हार परिवारों के साथ मिट्टी के दिए बनकर मनाई। उनके काम को नज़दीक से देखा, उनका हुनर सीखने की कोशिश की और उनकी तकलीफों और समस्याओं को समझा।

वो अपने घर नहीं जाते हैं - हम त्योहार खुशी से मना लें, वो थोड़े पैसे कमा लें, इसलिए अपना गांव, शहर, परिवार सब भूल जाते हैं।

वो मिट्टी से खुशियां बनाते हैं, दूसरों के पर्व को रौशन करते करते क्या खुद उजालों में जी पाते हैं? घरौंदे बनाने वाले अपने घर मुश्किल से चला पाते हैं!

दीवाली मतलब प्रकाश, जो गरीबी और मजबूरी का अंधेरा दूर कर पाए, जिसकी लौ में हर गृहस्थी मुस्कुराए। हमें एक ऐसा सिस्टम बनाना है - जो हुनर को हक़ और योगदान को सम्मान दिलाए - सबकी दिवाली, खुशियों वाली बनाए।

आशा करता हूं यह दिवाली आप सभी के किसी के जीवन में समृद्धि, तरक्की और मोहब्बत के कर आए।
#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #happydiwali, #happydiwali2024

In this video, we dive into the massive Singham Again box office collection of the highly anticipated film "Singham Again," directed by the visionary Rohit Shetty. With an ensemble star cast featuring Bollywood heavyweights Ajay Devgan, Akshay Kumar, Ranveer Singh, Tiger Shroff, Deepika Padukone, and Kareena Kapoor Khan, the film has taken the box office by storm. Not to forget, the special cameo of Chulbul Pandey by Salman Khan in Singham Again adds an extra layer of excitement!



Get ready for the ultimate action-packed cop drama with the blockbuster movie 'Singham Again' directed by Rohit Shetty. Starring an ensemble cast including Ajay Devgan, Akshay Kumar, Ranveer Singh, Tiger Shroff, Deepika Padukone, Kareena Kapoor, and a special cameo by Salman Khan as Chulbul Pandey, this Bollywood movie promises to keep you on the edge of your seat.

Singham Again Review: Fans and critics alike are raving about the adrenaline-pumping action sequences and powerful performances in Singham Again.

Singham Again Budget: The movie boasts a massive budget with top-notch production values, making it a visual treat for the audience.

Singham Again Worldwide Collection: With its widespread appeal and star-studded cast, Singham Again is expected to make waves at the global box office.

Singham Again Public Review: Audiences can't stop praising the stellar performances and high-octane action in Singham Again.

Singham Again 1st Day Collection: The film has shattered box office records on its opening day, setting the stage for a blockbuster run at the cinemas.

snippet.title: MIXTURE Snack | DIWALI Special Traditional Mixture Recipe Cooking In Village | South Indian Snacks
snippet.description:
Mixture Recipe is a popular snack recipe in South India, especially in Tamil Nadu, Kerala and Karnataka. Today, we are cooking this recipe as a Diwali Special. The specialty of this snack is its mixed taste. 

To enhance the flavor of this mixture, we use Boondi, Fried Nuts, Fried Spices, and other healthy ingredients, along with Omappodi.

The taste is memorable!
